  "founderStoryPage.phaseAStages[1].storylineClip.figureAlt": "Golden Buddha statue — atmosphere of the religious theatre described in Stage 2",
  "founderStoryPage.phaseAStages[2].label": "A 3",
  "founderStoryPage.phaseAStages[2].paragraphs[0]": "On **15 November 2020**, the **true identities** of the souls inside us and their **tricks** were finally exposed. In fear and rage we tried to **exorcise** them.",
